## Túnel localhost:8080

- Quick Tunnel: `npm run publish:trycloudflare` | URL: `TRYCLOUDFLARE-URL.txt`
- Verificación: `npm run tunnel:verify` (HTTP + 7 E2E en `:8080`)
- Sin ventanas cmd: `npm run tunnel:silence` | Desactivar: `npm run tunnel:disable`
- Helpers: `scripts/tunnel-helpers.ps1`, `tunnel-stack-start.ps1`
- Docs: `docs/CLOUDFLARE-TUNNEL.md`

